        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Over de auteurs</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Dr. Weifeng Chen is Universitair Docent Innovatiemanagement en Strategie aan de Brunel Business School, gespecialiseerd in AI-adoptie en digitale transformatie.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm">
